{{Infobox philosopher | name = J. Moufawad-Paul | image = | caption = | birth_date = | birth_place = | region = [[Western philosophy]] | era = 21st Century Philospohy | school_tradition = [[Marxism]], [[Maoism]] | main_interests = [[Dialectics]], [[Marxism]], [[Antagonistic Contradictions]] | education = [[York University]] <small>Phd. Philosophy</small> | institutions = [[York University]] | notable_ideas = ''"Continuity" and "Rupture"'' | influences = {{hlist |[[Mao Zedong|Mao]] | [[Alain Badiou|Badiou]], [[Karl Marx|Marx]], [[Huey Newton]], [[Slavoj Zizek]]}} | influenced = | website = }}
'''J. Moufawad-Paul''', Phd. is a Canadian academic, writer and blogger from Toronto, Canada. Dr. Moufawad-Paul is a [[Maoist]] philosopher and has written several works on the topic and regularly posts on his blog ''M-L-M Mayhem'', which focuses on the philosophy of [[Marxism-Leninism-Maoism]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://moufawad-paul.blogspot.com/p/about.html|title=About|publisher=}}</ref>{{Unreliable source?|date=December 2018|sure=yes}}<ref>{{cite web|url=https://yorku.academia.edu/JoshuaMoufawadPaul|title=Joshua Moufawad-Paul - York University - Academia.edu|website=yorku.academia.edu}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.zero-books.net/authors/joshua-r-moufawad-paul|title=J. Moufawad-Paul -- Zero Books -- Author Profile|website=www.zero-books.net}}</ref>
