'''Sawan Kirpal Ruhani Mission''' is a non-profit, spiritual organization.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.speakingtree.in/sant-rajinder-singh-ji-maharaj|title=Sant Rajinder Singh Ji Maharaj|website=Speaking Tree|access-date=9 September 2018}}</ref>
It is currently headed by ''[[Sant Rajinder Singh Ji Maharaj]]'' .<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.tribuneindia.com/2014/20140324/delhi.htm#9|title=Live life to be in love with God|last=About the Head of SKRM|first=|date=24 March 2014|work=Tribune India|access-date=9 September 2018}}</ref> The headquarters of ''Sawan Kirpal Ruhani Mission (SKRM)'' are based in [[Delhi]], [[India]].<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://articles.chicagotribune.com/1999-10-08/news/9910080280_1_sant-rajinder-singh-god-meditation|title=Meditating on God|last=SKRM Headquarters|first=By Michaek Ko|date=8 October 1999|work=Chicago Tribune|access-date=9 September 2018}}</ref> == Overview == ''Sawan Kirpal Ruhani Mission'' provides a forum for people to learn [[Meditation]], experience personal transformation and bring about inner and outer peace and human unity.<ref>{{Cite book|title=The Abode Of The Beloved|last=Rajinder Singh|publisher=SK Publications|year=2015|isbn=978-0-918224-78-1|location=4 S 175 Naperville Rd., Naperville, IL 60563|pages=149, 150}}</ref>
SKRM has over 2600 centers and its literature is available in more than 55 languages. The headquarters of the organization is in Vijay Nagar, Delhi.
