It also facilitates programs that provides a setting where people from around the world can learn to meditate.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/birmingham/content/articles/2008/04/18/spirituality_feature.shtml|title=Science of Spirituality in Birmingham|last=About the Activities|date=18 April 2008|work=BBC|access-date=9 September 2018}}</ref>
